Keratin Treatment FAQs ✨ a lot of you have recently been asking about my keratin treatment from @riccikapricci.salon so I wanted to answer some FAQs below: 

🤍How long does it last? All hair is different but for me it lasts about 6 months
🤍What does it do? It smooths out your hair to reduce frizz/flyaways
🤍Are you able to curl it still? Yes! After the initial set in period of a few days, you can wash it and style it however you desire
🤍How much does it cost? Prices vary by salon and area so check your local salon! 
🤍Where can I get it done? For my Chicago area girlies @riccikapricci.salon does an amazing job and they have locations throughout the city
